messages.text: Hello! I'm Clara, your virtual assistant for UtilityCo. I can help with billing, meter readings, appointments, and more, 24/7.

messages.text: Before we start, can I please confirm your account details? To proceed, please provide your Account Number or Full Postcode and House Number.

messages.text: My account number is 3887110 but I can't remember my postcode right now.

messages.speaker: Clara
messages.text: Are you, or anyone in your household, experiencing a difficult situation right now that might affect your energy/water use, payment, or ability to communicate? This is confidential.

messages.speaker: Customer
messages.text: No, everything's fine

messages.speaker: Clara
messages.text: Great. How can I help you today?
